 "awd_abstract_narration": "9804051\r\nConrad\r\nOne of the important issues in particle physics in recent decades has been the question of neutrino mass.  To date, no experiment has clearly measured a neutrino mass that is different from zero. This proposal requests construction funds for an experiment that will make a definitive measurement in a mass region where some indication of non-zero mass has been seen.  In addition, this experiment includes significant education/outreach components. \r\n",
